C.A. Lehnebach. (C.A.Lehnebach &amp; A.Zeller s.n., WELT SP092756/A).
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="0B98F2A300B42AAF21F46AF8DB93FA1F" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10167" pageId="7" pageNumber="60" start="Figure 4" startId="F4">
